The paper discusses a reinforcement learning problem and proposes a new approach that uses Bayesian optimization and Bayesian quadrature. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with the impact of environment variables, which suggests that it may also belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Finally, the paper uses Bayesian methods, which suggests that it may also belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
